data.name: labelMainContent.Text
data.value:
不幸的是，Game Studio崩溃了。 请通过发送有关此崩溃的信息来帮助我们改善Xenko。
如果您想让我们询问有关崩溃的一些问题，请输入您的电子邮件（可选，我们绝不会以任何其他原因向您发送电子邮件）
data.comment:
Unfortunately, Game Studio has crashed. Please help us improve Xenko by sending information about this crash.
If you'd like to allow us to ask some questions about the crash, please enter your email (optional, we will never send you an email for any other reason)
